                  , <rs id="t17890603-38-viclabel183" type="occupation">Esq.</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890603-38-victim346 t17890603-38-viclabel183"></join> about twelve in the night, on the <rs id="t17890603-38-cd184" type="crimeDate">18th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890603-38-off182 t17890603-38-cd184"></join> last, and burglariously stealing therein, three muslin handkerchiefs, value 7 s. 6 d. one hat, value 1 s. his property; and one velveret waistcoat, value 2 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17890603-38-victim348" type="victimName">
